  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help us expand our Thread of Hope Fund to serve refugee women and girls in Africa and teach them how to sew! What are they sewing? Menstrual Hygiene Kits, that last for 2-4 years and enable women and girls to live life freely, and earn back days of school and work. Nowhere is this more needed than refugee communities, which is why Days for Girls is focusing on expanding the Thread of Hope.</narrative>
